\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 The Core Idea\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0 Every team on earth is running their "workflow" across a graveyard of half-used tools:\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Slack for comms 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  Notion for docs 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  Trello for tasks 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  Airtable for data 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  Loom for updates 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  Calendly for meetings 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  Miro for thinking 
\f3 \uc0\u8594 
\f2  Google Drive for everything else\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b \cf0 Nobody talks to anything. Nothing is in one place. The workflow IS the problem.
\f2\b0 \
FlowStack is a single, living workspace where every workflow primitive \'97 task, decision, document, data, communication, approval, automation \'97 exists in one unified graph. Not integrated. Not connected via Zapier. 
\f1\b Natively one.
\f2\b0 \
The killer insight: 
\f1\b Workflow isn't a feature. It's the operating system. Nobody has built the OS yet.
\f2\b0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 The 7 Unified Primitives\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0 Everything in FlowStack is built from just 7 building blocks \'97 combined infinitely:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs26 \cf0 \uc0\u55357 \u56523 
\f4  TASK        
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f4  Assignable, trackable, deadlineable unit of work\

\f0 \uc0\u55357 \u56516 
\f4  DOC         
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f4  Living document that embeds tasks, data & decisions\

\f0 \uc0\u55357 \u56771 \u65039 
\f4   TABLE       
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f4  Structured data that triggers tasks & feeds docs\

\f0 \uc0\u55357 \u56492 
\f4  THREAD      
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f4  Contextual conversation attached to any primitive\

\f0 \uc0\u9989 
\f4  DECISION    
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f4  Logged, attributed, time-stamped choice with rationale\

\f0 \uc0\u9881 \u65039 
\f4   AUTOMATION  
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f4  If/then logic connecting any primitive to any other\

\f0 \uc0\u55357 \u56522 
\f4  PULSE       
\f5 \uc0\u8594 
\f4  Real-time status view across any combination of above\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs24 \cf0 Every other tool in existence is just 
\f1\b one of these seven things
\f2\b0  dressed up with a brand name and a $15/seat price tag.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

