\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs24 \cf0 Instead of switching apps, everything lives on a 
\f1\b spatial canvas
\f2\b0  where workflows are 
\f6\i drawn
\f2\i0 , not configured:\
