\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 The Organic Growth Engine \'97 3 Flywheels\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Flywheel 1 \'97 The Invite Cascade
\f2\b0  Every workflow naturally involves people outside the core team \'97 clients, contractors, agencies. Each gets a guest link. Each guest link is a conversion opportunity. Every workflow is a sales motion.\

\f1\b Flywheel 2 \'97 The Template Marketplace
\f2\b0  Users publish their workflows as templates. A "SaaS onboarding workflow" by a top-rated CS team gets downloaded 4,000 times. Creator gets revenue share. Platform gets distribution. Zero marketing spend.\

\f1\b Flywheel 3 \'97 The Workflow Showcase
\f2\b0  Teams make their workflow canvases public as case studies. 
\f6\i "How Stripe runs its incident response workflow."
\f2\i0  These get shared obsessively in operator communities \'97 each one a landing page for FlowStack.\
